Package org.qcri.rheem.core.optimizer.enumeration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PlanEnumerationPruningStrategy
    A strategy to prune PartialPlans from a PlanEnumeration.
    StageAssignmentTraversal.StageSplittingCriterion
    Criterion to futher split InterimStage besides precedence.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecutionPlanCreator
    Creates an PreliminaryExecutionPlan from a PartialPlan.
    ExecutionPlanCreator.Activation
    Propagates a Channel to its consumers.
    InternalOperatorPruningStrategy
    This PlanEnumerationPruningStrategy follows the idea that we can throw away a PartialPlan, when there is a further one that is (i) better and (ii) has the exact same operators with still-to-be-connected Slots.
    PartialPlan
    Represents a partial execution plan.
    PlanEnumeration
    Represents a collection of PartialPlans that all implement the same section of a RheemPlan (which is assumed to contain OperatorAlternatives in general).
    PlanEnumerator
    The plan partitioner recursively dissects a RheemPlan into PlanEnumerations and then assembles them.
    PreliminaryExecutionPlan
    Graph of ExecutionTasks and Channels.
    StageAssignmentTraversal
    Builds an ExecutionPlan from a PreliminaryExecutionPlan.
